13 Comparison with ‘org-pending’
********************************

Bruno Barbier's ‘org-pending’ is a closely related upstream Org patch
(branch ‘bba-pending-contents’) that nevertheless declares itself
independent of Org mode.  It solves a similar problem from a different
angle.

Aspect         ‘org-pending’                 ‘pending’
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Distribution   Org-mode patch                Standalone library
                                             
Org            None (but namespace and       None
dependency     prefix imply Org)             
State          ‘:scheduled → :pending →      Adds ‘:running’,
machine        :success/:failure’            ‘:streaming’, ‘:cancelled’,
                                             ‘:expired’
                                             
Animation      Static Unicode glyph          Animated spinner (10 fps,
                                             single global timer)
                                             
Progress bar   Single line of text in        Eighth-block Unicode bar
               ‘after-string’                (or ASCII fallback)
                                             
Streaming      Message-passing via           First-class
               ‘org-pending-send-update’     ‘pending-stream-insert’ /
                                             ‘-stream-finish’
                                             
Description    ‘*Region Lock*’ describe      Tabulated list (deferred
UI             buffer                        describe-buffer)
                                             
Indirect       Read-only projection          Not yet -- single-buffer
buffers                                      scope
                                             
Kill-emacs     Built in                      Same hook, gated by
query                                        ‘pending-confirm-on-emacs-exit’

   The two libraries can coexist.  Pick whichever suits your caller: if
you live in Org and want minimal animation, prefer ‘org-pending’; if you
want streaming and progress visualization out of the box, prefer
‘pending’.


